    "description": "一款第三人称多人/合作足球游戏，您可以在其中扮演俱乐部球员或经理的角色。 射门、传球、滑行、球旋转都由球员控制，而俱乐部标志、阵型、比赛中的比赛指令则来自教练。 简而言之，没有脚本游戏，没有手持。<br><strong>游戏玩法：</strong><br>比赛既可以作为游戏中的玩家进行，也可以作为球队的教练/经理进行，玩家和教练的游戏点数、等级都会受到您作为玩家扮演的角色或您作为教练所做的决定的影响。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/d3112fda0f79578b527aeada1315b685.poster.avif?t=1757055020\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/d3112fda0f79578b527aeada1315b685.webm?t=1757055020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/d3112fda0f79578b527aeada1315b685.mp4?t=1757055020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>机制：</strong><br>  作为一名球员，射门、传球、球旋转不像传统的足球视频游戏那样是自动的或脚本化的，但球员可以控制踢球的角度以及球旋转的类型，从而使球产生不同的运动。 球旋转不仅限于射门和传球，还可以用于控球情况和各种游戏技巧（发挥您的想象力）。 这些使得游戏玩法非常动态、不可预测且基于技能。 场内玩家不能创建多人比赛，只能加入。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/4b1321a29476c9c4d16fa8770b73275d.poster.avif?t=1757055020\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/4b1321a29476c9c4d16fa8770b73275d.webm?t=1757055020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/4b1321a29476c9c4d16fa8770b73275d.mp4?t=1757055020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>应该注意的是，前提是玩家头像与游戏原型相关，这些原型会影响您在比赛中的使用方式。 例如：在担任防守角色时使用大个子球员有助于轻松剥夺较轻的前锋（假设对方前锋决定使用较轻的球员以提高速度）。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/f661baffeed12b4353326cc16e4ff2d2.poster.avif?t=1757055020\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/f661baffeed12b4353326cc16e4ff2d2.webm?t=1757055020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/f661baffeed12b4353326cc16e4ff2d2.mp4?t=1757055020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>作为一名教练，您肩负着建立俱乐部、阵型、战术、邀请球员加入、创建比赛以及指导/管理您的团队取得成功的责任。 比赛中做出的决定（好或坏）会影响您在赛季教练排名中的俱乐部级别、排名和教练声誉。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/9a10a4ecc718fb15c1b3c42e441449a8.poster.avif?t=1757055020\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/9a10a4ecc718fb15c1b3c42e441449a8.webm?t=1757055020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/9a10a4ecc718fb15c1b3c42e441449a8.mp4?t=1757055020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/1502000fec537ee63d187181768cdaa7.poster.avif?t=1757055020\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/1502000fec537ee63d187181768cdaa7.webm?t=1757055020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/1502000fec537ee63d187181768cdaa7.mp4?t=1757055020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>其他：</strong><br>球员可以自由定制他们的球员头像外观、俱乐部标志、俱乐部颜色、球衣等。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/732af6cca6262a4722e518aaf997a2a1.poster.avif?t=1757055020\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/732af6cca6262a4722e518aaf997a2a1.webm?t=1757055020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/732af6cca6262a4722e518aaf997a2a1.mp4?t=1757055020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/a7efd6aa30782f09cd52cb3cf69ba672.poster.avif?t=1757055020\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/a7efd6aa30782f09cd52cb3cf69ba672.webm?t=1757055020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/a7efd6aa30782f09cd52cb3cf69ba672.mp4?t=1757055020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>抢断、头球、盯人都遵循游戏玩法部分所述的完全控制原则。 因此，玩家可以控制他们铲球的极限，并反过来根据场景证明黄牌或红牌的合理性，甚至更好的是，玩家会因完美定时的铲球、远距离射门等而获得奖励。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/8437ae8c5494a986262e778819f57b69.poster.avif?t=1757055020\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/8437ae8c5494a986262e778819f57b69.webm?t=1757055020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299480/extras/8437ae8c5494a986262e778819f57b69.mp4?t=1757055020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
